  "reference_number": "RUS1976",
  "remarks": "\nOleg Georgevich SHAPOVALOV is an \"involved person\" under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 because he is the Minister of Justice for the so-called Republic of Crimea. Through his role as Minister of Justice, SHAPOVALOV is or has: been responsible for, engaged in, provided support for, or promoted policies and actions which destabilise Ukraine and undermine or threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine.\n",
